snippet.title: Jimeva Crime Time
snippet.description:
My channel is based around the 
Chris Watts Family Murders Case & True Crime. 
Everyone in the world is confused 
by all the missing pieces in this case.
I love digging a little deeper into the 
FACTS to help everyone understand 
different perspectives. 
Keep in mind I'm a VERY open-minded
person so as long your respectful to 
me I will be graciously respectful to you.
Disrespectful individuals will be blocked & deleted. 
We all want justice for Shanann, Bella, Celeste & Niko! 
💜💜💜💜
God bless the Rzucek's!!! 

I appreciate your love & support!
God Bless!
